---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: "Notes on learning vocabulary that sticks: spaced repetition, retrieval practice, word nuance, and what we're building in Lexi."
permalink: /blog/
---
<h1>Blog</h1>
<p class="lede">Notes on learning vocabulary that sticks — the science, the
words themselves, and what we're building in Lexi.</p>
<ul class="post-list">
  {% for p in collections.posts | reverse %}
  <li>
    <a href="{{ p.url }}">{{ p.data.title }}</a>
    <span class="muted">{{ p.date | readableDate }}</span>
    {% if p.data.description %}<p class="muted">{{ p.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
  </li>
  {% else %}
  <li class="muted">First posts landing soon.</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
